song_lyrics: Pankhī banu to ūḍyā karu, mārā Swāmīne laīne ūḍyā karu... Mane° ṭek
Sasalu banu to doḍyā karu, mārā Swāmīnī pāchhaḷ doḍyā karu... Mane° ṭek
Fūlaḍu banu to mahekyā karu, mārā Swāmīnā hārmā mahekyā karu... Mane° ṭek
Koyal banu to gāyā karu, mārā Swāmīnā guṇlā gāyā karu... Mane° ṭek
title: Mane em thāy ke

2-2004: Sadhu Achalmunidas
